{"tid":1558203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跳閘運動唔成功因為唔夠人多","createTime":"2019-09-10T11:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T12:43:27.000Z","uid":27210,"like":87,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"04bac6e75480d6c5ca31b865200b0fcc78f980cf","tid":1558203,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你班撚樣，唔撚記得咗黨鐵點對我地？<br />\n太子站死咗人呀，死咗人呀！<br />\n你日日搭既列車都分分鐘沾滿鮮血！<br />\n仲俾錢佢賺？！<br />\n<br />\n我地已經唔係最前線面對黑社會同popo！如果對藍絲，黨鐵職員都唔敢，仲抗乜撚野爭？<br />\n<br />\n一蚊都唔好俾黨鐵！轉咗搭巴士既轉返番黎！繼續跳閘同保護手足！<br />\n推到萬人跳閘！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b014e46fda50df96323da89a89b9cbc9cca3b9","tid":1558203,"uid":264717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4HTe8zi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4HTe8zi.jpg&h=cfb956af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SaEAei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SaEAei.jpg&h=f6e82dfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6e24e8c5d7f757afcf8a9cb81e6162f95bcc54c","tid":1558203,"uid":234159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFb8tFf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFb8tFf.jpg&h=67608619&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93fcbddbda9e97fa6013a425ccfe53ef5b5d1a65","tid":1558203,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e48768721f38a5dcf3128ad1b7ffb3c208530fd","tid":1558203,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072acc56d41d82ed9bb79c2980fa174f0d6766be","tid":1558203,"uid":143699,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:26:37.000Z","msg":"老實講，其實跳閘大家都識，真係唔難。但困難嘅係要點要跨過自已嘅心理關口，一旦你跨過咗，跳閘對你嚟講真係easy job。<br />\n<br />\n我知道好多巴絲打都會擔心跳閘嘅時侯會被港鐵職員捉，驚會罰錢呀，又可能會犯法呀咁。但我想同大家講真係唔洗驚，因為係唔會架！你地睇完呢條片就知。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[全民乘搭港鐵優惠] <br />\n應對職員方法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yHVLw9-1k9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyHVLw9-1k9A&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4Rzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=6f0f6c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yHVLw9-1k9A</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n優惠卷poster：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGZxvwU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGZxvwU.jpg&h=aa7704ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到今時今日，大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘。<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先我地重溫一下最基本嘅三種跳法先：</span></span><br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平日訓練：</span></span><br />\n大家可以係公園嘅呢啲健身器材到練習。其實正常人應該都做到動作一，你用呢個雙桿熟習下個動作，到落場跳就會輕鬆好多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSK69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSK69.jpg&h=21c80ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於動作二可以由低至高嘅障礙物慢慢練起，最緊要係起手動作，雙手配合身體擺動，跳起時心胸盡量貼緊膝頭<br />\n<br />\n動作三就周圍都練到，搵啲單邊嘅欄杆都得。同埋唔一定要單手，雙手都做到同樣效果。係冇咁有型姐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">注意事項：</span></span><br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">－最近黨鐵多咗狗，如果情況唔允許，希望大家都唔好勉強，可以改用老人卡。唔好因為咁而被人捉。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n完整跳閘教學示範片段： <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4Rzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=6c751aca\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"cdc8edcf52ffbaea446a4b8368033f028aa17650","tid":1558203,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8940c00