家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"bc866cef67b8ff53187cbcca85ba6868226c1ebb","tid":1558203,"uid":4559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:23:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b060f6bde7e6077bd7fead9b95830329769f13c3","tid":1558203,"uid":34029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"係D人唔夠團結 同 淆底<br />\n支持加價到50蚊一程好過LA"},{"pid":"ed3f393d3e7c6555e8803841b8f89db8818b43af","tid":1558203,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b060f6bde7e6077bd7fead9b95830329769f13c3","tid":1558203,"uid":34029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"係D人唔夠團結 同 淆底<br />\n支持加價到50蚊一程好過LA"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477f967b3595926ee61894213f56f7b7203808d5","tid":1558203,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc866cef67b8ff53187cbcca85ba6868226c1ebb","tid":1558203,"uid":4559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:23:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723a6598c373ee8e44c58664025ac29375c5fb79","tid":1558203,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzKYXAf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzKYXAf.png&h=c44ec0b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n護身符，張飛好似係7月旺角遊行嗰日有人比我，我話我會跳閘走，不過佢都照比我，最後好似坐放學車走用唔著，依家隨身帶住當跳閘護身符"},{"pid":"bb768ad9d8d91dda49445b3d61f5c8c14ff28571","tid":1558203,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"搭開嘅車站都係開合閘機<br />\n基本上都唔駛跳 貼住人過就得<br />\n神